WEBVTT

00:00:02.430 --> 00:00:05.853
Ovaj zvuk,

00:00:05.853 --> 00:00:09.588
ovaj miris,

00:00:09.588 --> 00:00:13.693
ovaj prizor

00:00:13.693 --> 00:00:17.221
sve me podseća na logorske
vatre mog detinjstva,

00:00:17.221 --> 00:00:24.617
kad je svako mogao postati pripovedač
ispred plamena koji pleše.

00:00:24.617 --> 00:00:27.540
Postojao je čudesan kraj

00:00:27.540 --> 00:00:32.106
kada bi i ljudi i vatra zaspali
gotovo u istom trenutku.